EXTRACTED VALUE: Ivy stopped talking on the phone, and after she and Jenks exchanged a look, she clicked it off without saying good-bye. "Who is Minias?"
"Very little," said Anselmo scornfully. "Very little in my judgment. To steal, yes. To eat well, yes. To murder, yes. To fight, no."
"What does that say?" she demanded of Madilla, her nursemaid.
"What do you mean?" asked Sister Julienne.
